    Author:
    Devin S. Olsonm (dolson@czarnowski.com)
    See Also:
    "RFC822: Standard for ARPA Internet Text Messages" http://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc822/, Serialized Form

      • buildAddr822Full

        public static String buildAddr822Full(String phrase,
                                      String addr821,
                                      String... comments)
        Generates an RFC822 Addr822Full Address String from the specified component parts.
        Parameters:
        phrase - Addr822Phrase part used to construct the result.
        addr821 - Addr821 part used to construct the result.
        comments - Addr822Comment1, Addr822Comment2, and Addr822Comment2 parts used to construct the result.
        Returns:
        properly formatted RFC822 Addr822Full string generated from the component parts. Empty string on error or no value for addr821.
